<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-18690] New consumer doesn&apos;t updateLatestMetadata for topics matching new regex</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-18690</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the consumer subscribes to the new RE2J regex resolved on the broker, it&apos;s not keeping the leader and epoch info from the metadata response, so not able to properly update the fetch positions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After getting the assignment with the topics matching the regex, and receiving the topics in a metadata response, the consumer is not retaining topics that are assigned with Re2Jpattern so fails with&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
Leader for partition {} is unknown for fetching offset {}&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
This seems to be the reason behind it, not retaining topics assigned with RE2J&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/d19b60521001697bc9d518cfc3d585e7b78d15a3/clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/ConsumerMetadata.java#L97&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/d19b60521001697bc9d518cfc3d585e7b78d15a3/clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/ConsumerMetadata.java#L97&#160;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So when handling the metadata response that includes the matching topics it will never make it to update the leader/epoch info.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/d19b60521001697bc9d518cfc3d585e7b78d15a3/clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/Metadata.java#L521&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/d19b60521001697bc9d518cfc3d585e7b78d15a3/clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/Metadata.java#L521&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To validate with should end with a test similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/d19b60521001697bc9d518cfc3d585e7b78d15a3/core/src/test/scala/integration/kafka/api/PlaintextConsumerSubscriptionTest.scala#L251&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/d19b60521001697bc9d518cfc3d585e7b78d15a3/core/src/test/scala/integration/kafka/api/PlaintextConsumerSubscriptionTest.scala#L251&lt;/a&gt; but including consumption.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
